Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:58.85,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:58.85,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:04.85,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,くるくる廻る天道虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:04.85,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Ladybug going round and round
