Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647.408,434.92)}Ten: Tenho-doori no Kaidanji\N(The Nice Guy on Tenho Way)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:32.65,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That strange atmosphere just now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling that something passed between Ten and Nakanishi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi's initial joy was a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A flickering vision of victory
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he do that often?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm two tiles away from a Kokusi Musou hand!\NAnd if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have just about won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, I'm sorry but the power is in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. This isn't what I want
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And not this either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,5,200 points
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheeeit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was one Wan tile from Tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he throw away a double sided wait by discarding 6 and 7 sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten was waiting for them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I see.\NBy leaving the 1 Man and West tiles in his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't eliminate the possibility of me finishing my Kokusi Musou
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was giving me... HOPE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had seen through your strategy, pops
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't win another game
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.15,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,4th Game\NEast Hand 4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points from everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi's round as dealer is over
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all tied up at two games to two
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you forgotten about winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no excuse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I take responsibility for what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had in my hands such a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop that style of play
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But just a little longer and I would have had a Kokusi Musou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let that situation pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at it all wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of half baked thinking is fatal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeful imaginings will absolutely be taken advantage of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope allows them to get what they want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the majority of people that's a okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,HOWEVER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In gambling it's just the opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose everthing because of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrust it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So. The power, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And not just the wall switch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the circuit breaker watched as well
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's signature move is slight of hand in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Tenhou Chuuren Poutou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.\NI'll have the young guys watch them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard all the power to this room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some safety in holding off his rough cheating
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And their coordinated play is reduced to dust
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's pathway to victory is entirely destroyed, isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems likely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.18,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NEast Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're disoriented because of Nakanishi's rash behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten is still an unknown quantity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,1,300/2,600 points
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.51,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NEast Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.68,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NSouth Hand 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000/4,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're catching up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He ain't so easily understood
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. My brain is tired\NI need something sweet to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go get me a Daihuku rice cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.55,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NSouth Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't count on THAT hand just yet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,16,00 points
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current points are enough to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Last hand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last hand, Ten is dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it's Ten's last chance to pull his Tenhou Chuuren Poutou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't cut the power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,TEN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Breh, somebody snuck in next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU TRYING TO CHEAT ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those tiles don't count
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a do-over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We know about your Chuuren PouTou shit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow you managed to put the lights out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but by no means will we accept this situation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I just now cheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We doubt you at the very least
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen and listen well
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I've cheated or not
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't air half baked suspicions
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We, and everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we fought this 5th battle with all we had
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,thus at this, the 11th hour
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no reason for vague accusations
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This Mahjong game we've been playing has been true gambling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it not been a fair contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I've got a Chuuren PouTou or not
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,over any suspicions raised
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if no cheating can be confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the old man's Deed with me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead serious
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've cheated do as you like, but on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't cheat we've won
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already decided you cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten hasn't cheated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The daihuku rice cake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dahuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Ten ate from the daihuku
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In his slight of hand, he exchanges his 14 tiles with the first tile wall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he pulled that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be powder stuck to the tiles in the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But that powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's none on the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We can't say it's suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. If that's the case, can we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,TENHOU CHUUREN POUTOU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We win
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever do that stuff again
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I PROMISE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether by guile or cheating outright
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to win by any means necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he switch them with only his LEFT hand, the one without powder on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see it at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho Doori\N(Tenho Street)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh. It can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,More than that, I've got something for you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you be a ringer for me once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You played a mean game
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fought those older than yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Each side has a pair of ringers in a total score match
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the representative that comes first is the victor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't end for me like this
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. Heh heh heh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks for this as well
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is another of our ringers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your consideration\N(Kansai dialect)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our ringers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's a ringer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time. Let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:37.01,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,East Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Chitoitsu\N(all pairs hand)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He turns down each pair as he completes them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.85,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,East Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoitsu, Tanyao.\N(All pairs, tiles numbered 2-8)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A chitoitsu again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he read my discards?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.64,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,South Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He ought not be able to read this surplus tile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,unless he can peek into my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be like he's got some superpower
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.\NA chitoitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THA FUUU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another chitoitsu?\NWaiting on a 3 Sou (bamboo)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how?\NIs it by mere chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I tell you the trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes betray you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:52.09,Default - top,,0,0,0,,When the tile you want comes out your eyes follow it for an instant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:56.64,Default - top,,0,0,0,,And what do you think happens to the tile you're drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:01.07,Default - top,,0,0,0,,When you discarded the 4 Sou, you, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:07.29,Default - top,,0,0,0,,drew your next tile with your middle finger, but it slid
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:10.47,Default - top,,0,0,0,,That is to say your eye-line shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:13.35,Default - top,,0,0,0,,and the tile you draw slid to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.35,0:24:15.35,Default - top,,0,0,0,,S-something so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:19.78,Default - top,,0,0,0,,It's ALL in the details
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:24.58,Default - top,,0,0,0,,That's the Mahjong level I'm at, kid
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.58,0:24:34.72,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Quite an interesting game you're having, isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.44,0:24:39.58,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.58,0:24:44.61,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Won't you let me mix it up a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:25:09.11,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,Next Episode:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:24:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true all the world round...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.55,0:25:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever crumbles under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,has no path to victory
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,AKAGI SHIGERU
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's never been beaten
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A peerless Mahjong professional
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.68,0:25:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Ten?
